40cb80f7ba6a21364962257fa337eaec83bbe698","tid":21060,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:51:18.000Z","msg":"俾件英奸走狗上到位真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75fed31baa7b7243298ab059243cf55bc8a8e04","tid":21060,"uid":21014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T19:13:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日睇佢上唔清唔楚啲嘴臉真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係滿口歪理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不斷滑坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有睇佢上唔清唔楚<br />\n論點根本就自打嘴巴 up得就up<br />\n<br />\n一開波話咩野 如果唔同港獨畫清界線 <br />\n什至同佢地做朋友  咁俾人感覺係同一派 <br />\n都係一樣支持港獨<br />\n<br />\n跟住主持問佢 <br />\n依家地區直選非建制拎到一半以上席位<br />\n咁係唔係代表左市民其實係支持佔中 <br />\n點知條7頭話唔係  重申香港人係唔支持佔中<br />\n因為非建制都唔係打住支持佔中依個排頭黎參選<br />\n所以投佢地唔等於支持<br />\n<br />\n我心諗屌你老母啦 <br />\n大多數泛民都有參與佔中<br />\n又有去演練 <br />\n投得佢地個D人 米姐係某個程支持囉 <br />\n<br />\n條友都on99  自打嘴巴"},{"pid":"a8391e6e059a3a736f72ae8e091e240406420eec","tid":21060,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T19:34:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"b86b03c5ab9c48a2c05438029b4a971717075af7","tid":21060,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:17:14.000Z","msg":"佢做到特首都唔出奇"},{"pid":"10031c3ef1b47014ff6806d191e35953f744bcb9","tid":21060,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:55:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢做到特首都唔出奇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n689後嘅傀儡？"}]}